  <p>The Company grants you a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license
     to access and use the Service solely for automating invoice creation and
     related bookkeeping tasks within your own QuickBooks Online company.</p>

  <h2>2. Restrictions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You may not sublicense, resell, or make the Service available to third parties.</li>
    <li>You may not reverse-engineer, copy, or modify the Service except as
